manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: Are you tired of your child constantly occupying your phone? Concerned about unsupervised internet access and their constant desire to join dad's gaming sessions? Worry no more! Our specially designed Android 13 Tablet for kids is here to put your concerns to rest. 10.1" 1280 x 800 resolution IPS LCD scratch-resistant touchscreen Android 13 Operating System- Android 13 is optimised for how you use your kids tablet. Giving you powerful device controls. Ande easier ways to manage conversations, privacy settings and so much more. Faster CPU-with a 2.0 GHz Octa Core Processor and 4 GB RAM enables quick app launches, smooth videos. Longer Lasting Battery 8000mAh- 18 hours mix use tablet time. 64GB Storage can be expanded up to 2TB via microSD card slot. Easy-to-use Parental Control- Pre-installed Family Link App Multiple Ways for Eye Protection- 10.1" 1280 x 800 IPS HD display better for your little ones' eyes. 2MP+5MP Camera- Video chat or snap selfies on the 2MP front camera and 5MP rear camera, or document your day on the rear camera and share to social media on the ultra-fast Wi-Fi. Ideal Gift for kids- It's a wonderful gift tablet for children’s birthdays, school supplies, Thanksgiving, Christmas, other holidays.

Note: Excellent Performance with Android 13 System: The 10" GMS-certified tablet, which runs the Android 13.0 Operating System, comes with Google Play Store and with its 4GB RAM and powerful and durable Octa-core processor, is faster and more responsive than other tablets. These features also enable quick APP launches, fluid light games and videos, and excellent overall performance. 4GB RAM 64GB ROM ( expandable to 2TB ), you can download movies and cartoons for your kids. Comes with Google Kids Space, a kids mode with content to help your child discover, create, and grow. A tablet experience with a custom home screen and library of quality content for children. Your child has the ability to customize their experience with unique avatars and receive content recommendations based on their interests, while parents can set boundaries with Family Link parental controls.

2MP + 5MP Dual Camera With the 2MP front-facing camera and 5MP rear camera. which enables children to capture every happy moments at anytime anyplace. This kids tablet is also perfect for video chatting, photos and selfies. Dual Protection With Kids-Proof Case This kids tablet adopt high quality silicone portective case that can avoid damages caused by drops and bumps at play. Friendly design with a stand, used as a tablet holder and more comfortable for childs to hold the tablet. 4GB RAM +64GB ROM ( Up to 2TB) 4GB RAM 64GB ROM, you can expand the storage to 2TB of SD cards for storing photos, music and videos with additional micro SD card extensions.

2.4G /5G Wi-Fi & BT5.0 Experience effortless connectivity and seamless sharing with our tablet's 2.4G + 5G Dual-Wi-Fi and power-saving BT5.0 technology, designed for the ultimate convenience. Longer Battery Life 8000mAh With its 8000mAh battery, you can enjoy up to 18 hours of reading, watching movies, and surfing the web. It is a great companion for your child to play and learn. Featuring fast charging technology, this kids tablet can be fully charged in 1.5 hours when using the 5V 2A charger provided. 360 Eye-Protection, 1280x800 IPS HD Screen High resolution bring more protections to kids eyes health, kids tablet adopts 1280x800 IPS HD touch screen display to present with vivid colors for a more true-to-life viewing experience at all angles. with adjustable back kickstand which will prevent kids from watching screen or play video game for a long time, it will give your child a whole protection on theirs eyes

The setup took ages we can't factory reset the tablet. We downloaded the family link, but it says there are no accounts linked.🤔 We may have done something wrong during the initial setup, but we're returning this
